From a90437db9bdf16cdfe13558ee1de3be6e4d92aca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Leonardo Mendes <Leonardo.MendesSantana@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 09:59:31 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add email support to ldap users

Add support for the `mail` attribute when creating local users.
Users can now be created with a default or custom email address.

Signed-off-by: Leonardo Mendes <Leonardo.MendesSantana@windriver.com>
---
 Makefile                  |  4 +--
 man/man1/ldapsetupemail.1 | 45 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 sbin/ldapsetupemail       | 82 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 sbin/ldapusersetup        | 28 +++++++++++++--
 4 files changed, 154 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 man/man1/ldapsetupemail.1
 create mode 100644 sbin/ldapsetupemail

