+.TH ldapsetupemail 1 "April 30, 2026"
+
+.SH NAME
+ldapsetupemail \- add or replace the email attribute of an LDAP user.
+
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+.B ldapsetupemail
+.RB <username | uid>
+.RB <email>
+
+.SH OPTIONS
+.TP
+.B [-u <username | uid> <email>]
+The name or uid of the user to add the email account.
+
+.SH "SEE ALSO"
+ldapdeleteuser(1), ldapaddgroup(1), ldapaddusertogroup(1), ldapmodifyuser(1), ldapscripts(5).
+
